{"id":353,"ayahs":[{"number":28,"arabic":"فَإِن لَّمْ تَجِدُوا۟ فِيهَآ أَحَدًۭا فَلَا تَدْخُلُوهَا حَتَّىٰ يُؤْذَنَ لَكُمْ ۖ وَإِن قِيلَ لَكُمُ ٱرْجِعُوا۟ فَٱرْجِعُوا۟ ۖ هُوَ أَزْكَىٰ لَكُمْ ۚ وَٱللَّهُ بِمَا تَعْمَلُونَ عَلِيمٌۭ","translation":"Hence, [even] if you find no one within [the house], do not enter it until you are given leave; and if you are told, “Turn back,” then turn back. This will be most conducive to your purity; and God has full knowledge of all that you do.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2819.mp3","surahId":24,"words":[{"id":31032,"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِن","translation":"তবে যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31033,"position":2,"arabic":"لَّمْ","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31034,"position":3,"arabic":"تَجِدُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা পাও","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31035,"position":4,"arabic":"فِيهَآ","translation":"তার মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31036,"position":5,"arabic":"أَحَدًۭا","translation":"কাউকে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31037,"position":6,"arabic":"فَلَا","translation":"তাহ'লে না","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31038,"position":7,"arabic":"تَدْخُلُوهَا","translation":"তাতে তোমরা প্রবেশ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31039,"position":8,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰ","translation":"যতক্ষণ না","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31040,"position":9,"arabic":"يُؤْذَنَ","translation":"অনুমতি দেয়া হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31041,"position":10,"arabic":"لَكُمْ ۖ","translation":"তোমাদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31043,"position":11,"arabic":"وَإِن","translation":"আর যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31044,"position":12,"arabic":"قِيلَ","translation":"বলা হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31045,"position":13,"arabic":"لَكُمُ","translation":"তোমাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31046,"position":14,"arabic":"ٱرْجِعُوا۟","translation":"\"তোমরা ফিরে যাও\"","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31047,"position":15,"arabic":"فَٱرْجِعُوا۟ ۖ","translation":"তাহ'লে তোমরা ফিরে যাও","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31049,"position":16,"arabic":"هُوَ","translation":"তা","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31050,"position":17,"arabic":"أَزْكَىٰ","translation":"পবিত্রতম","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31051,"position":18,"arabic":"لَكُمْ ۚ","translation":"জন্যে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31053,"position":19,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"আর আল্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31054,"position":20,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"ঐ বিষয়ে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31055,"position":21,"arabic":"تَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"তোমরা করো (সে সম্পর্কে)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31056,"position":22,"arabic":"عَلِيمٌۭ","translation":"খুব অবহিত","audioUrl":"wbw/024_028_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31057,"position":23,"arabic":"٢٨","translation":"(২৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":29,"arabic":"لَّيْسَ عَلَيْكُمْ جُنَاحٌ أَن تَدْخُلُوا۟ بُيُوتًا غَيْرَ مَسْكُونَةٍۢ فِيهَا مَتَٰعٌۭ لَّكُمْ ۚ وَٱللَّهُ يَعْلَمُ مَا تُبْدُونَ وَمَا تَكْتُمُونَ","translation":"[On the other hand,] you will incur no sin if you [freely] enter houses not intended for living in but serving a purpose useful to you: but [always remember that] God knows all that you do openly, and all that you would conceal.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2820.mp3","surahId":24,"words":[{"id":31996,"position":1,"arabic":"لَّيْسَ","translation":"নেই","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31997,"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31998,"position":3,"arabic":"جُنَاحٌ","translation":"কোন পাপ","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31999,"position":4,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32000,"position":5,"arabic":"تَدْخُلُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা প্রবেশ করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32001,"position":6,"arabic":"بُيُوتًا","translation":"(এমন) ঘরগুলোতে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32002,"position":7,"arabic":"غَيْرَ","translation":"(যা) নয়","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32003,"position":8,"arabic":"مَسْكُونَةٍۢ","translation":"বসবাসের স্থান (কারো)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32004,"position":9,"arabic":"فِيهَا","translation":"তার মধ্যে (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32005,"position":10,"arabic":"مَتَـٰعٌۭ","translation":"সামগ্রী দ্রব্য","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32006,"position":11,"arabic":"لَّكُمْ ۚ","translation":"তোমাদের (সবার জন্যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32008,"position":12,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"আর আল্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32009,"position":13,"arabic":"يَعْلَمُ","translation":"জানেন","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32010,"position":14,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32011,"position":15,"arabic":"تُبْدُونَ","translation":"তোমরা প্রকাশ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32012,"position":16,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"আর যা","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32013,"position":17,"arabic":"تَكْتُمُونَ","translation":"তোমরা গোপন করো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_029_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32014,"position":18,"arabic":"٢٩","translation":"(২৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":30,"arabic":"قُل لِّلْمُؤْمِنِينَ يَغُضُّوا۟ مِنْ أَبْصَٰرِهِمْ وَيَحْفَظُوا۟ فُرُوجَهُمْ ۚ ذَٰلِكَ أَزْكَىٰ لَهُمْ ۗ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ خَبِيرٌۢ بِمَا يَصْنَعُونَ","translation":"Tell the believing men to lower their gaze and to be mindful of their chastity: this will be most con­ducive to their purity – [and,] verily, God is aware of all that they do.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2821.mp3","surahId":24,"words":[{"id":33143,"position":1,"arabic":"قُل","translation":"(হে নাবী) বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_030_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33144,"position":2,"arabic":"لِّلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","translation":"মু'মিনদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_030_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33145,"position":3,"arabic":"يَغُضُّوا۟","translation":"সংযত করে (যেন তারা)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_030_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33146,"position":4,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"ব্যাপার","audioUrl":"wbw/024_030_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33147,"position":5,"arabic":"أَبْصَـٰرِهِمْ","translation":"দৃষ্টিগুলোর তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/024_030_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33148,"position":6,"arabic":"وَيَحْفَظُوا۟","translation":"এবং সংরক্ষণ করে (যেন)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_030_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33149,"position":7,"arabic":"فُرُوجَهُمْ ۚ","translation":"লজ্জাস্থানসমূহকে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/024_030_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33151,"position":8,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এটা","audioUrl":"wbw/024_030_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33152,"position":9,"arabic":"أَزْكَىٰ","translation":"পবিত্রতম","audioUrl":"wbw/024_030_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33153,"position":10,"arabic":"لَهُمْ ۗ","translation":"জন্যে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/024_030_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33155,"position":11,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/024_030_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33156,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":"wbw/024_030_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33157,"position":13,"arabic":"خَبِيرٌۢ","translation":"খুব অবগত","audioUrl":"wbw/024_030_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33158,"position":14,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"(ঐ বিষয়ে) যা কিছু","audioUrl":"wbw/024_030_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33159,"position":15,"arabic":"يَصْنَعُونَ","translation":"তারা করে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_030_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33160,"position":16,"arabic":"٣٠","translation":"(৩০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":31,"arabic":"وَقُل لِّلْمُؤْمِنَٰتِ يَغْضُضْنَ مِنْ أَبْصَٰرِهِنَّ وَيَحْفَظْنَ فُرُوجَهُنَّ وَلَا يُبْدِينَ زِينَتَهُنَّ إِلَّا مَا ظَهَرَ مِنْهَا ۖ وَلْيَضْرِبْنَ بِخُمُرِهِنَّ عَلَىٰ جُيُوبِهِنَّ ۖ وَلَا يُبْدِينَ زِينَتَهُنَّ إِلَّا لِبُعُولَتِهِنَّ أَوْ ءَابَآئِهِنَّ أَوْ ءَابَآءِ بُعُولَتِهِنَّ أَوْ أَبْنَآئِهِنَّ أَوْ أَبْنَآءِ بُعُولَتِهِنَّ أَوْ إِخْوَٰنِهِنَّ أَوْ بَنِىٓ إِخْوَٰنِهِنَّ أَوْ بَنِىٓ أَخَوَٰتِهِنَّ أَوْ نِسَآئِهِنَّ أَوْ مَا مَلَكَتْ أَيْمَٰنُهُنَّ أَوِ ٱلتَّٰبِعِينَ غَيْرِ أُو۟لِى ٱلْإِرْبَةِ مِنَ ٱلرِّجَالِ أَوِ ٱلطِّفْلِ ٱلَّذِينَ لَمْ يَظْهَرُوا۟ عَلَىٰ عَوْرَٰتِ ٱلنِّسَآءِ ۖ وَلَا يَضْرِبْنَ بِأَرْجُلِهِنَّ لِيُعْلَمَ مَا يُخْفِينَ مِن زِينَتِهِنَّ ۚ وَتُوبُوٓا۟ إِلَى ٱللَّهِ جَمِيعًا أَيُّهَ ٱلْمُؤْمِنُونَ لَعَلَّكُمْ تُفْلِحُونَ","translation":"And tell the believing women to lower their gaze and to be mindful of their chastity, and not to display their charms [in public] beyond what may [decently] be apparent thereof; hence, let them draw their head-coverings over their bosoms. And let them not display [more of] their charms to any but their husbands, or their fathers, or their husbands’ fathers, or their sons, or their husbands’ Sons, or their brothers, or their brothers’ sons, or their sisters’ sons, or their womenfolk, or those whom they rightfully possess, or such male attendants as are beyond all sexual desire, or children that are as yet unaware of women’s nakedness; and let them not swing their legs [in walking] so as to draw attention to their hidden charms And [always], O you believers - all of you - turn unto God in repentance, so that you might attain to a happy state!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2822.mp3","surahId":24,"words":[{"id":34141,"position":1,"arabic":"وَقُل","translation":"এবং বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_031_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34142,"position":2,"arabic":"لِّلْمُؤْمِنَـٰتِ","translation":"মু'মিন নারীদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_031_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34143,"position":3,"arabic":"يَغْضُضْنَ","translation":"তারা সংযত রাখে (যেন)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_031_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34144,"position":4,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"ব্যাপার","audioUrl":"wbw/024_031_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34145,"position":5,"arabic":"أَبْصَـٰرِهِنَّ","translation":"তাদের দৃষ্টিসমূহের","audioUrl":"wbw/024_031_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34146,"position":6,"arabic":"وَيَحْفَظْنَ","translation":"ও সংরক্ষণ করে (যেন)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_031_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34147,"position":7,"arabic":"فُرُوجَهُنَّ","translation":"তাদের লজ্জাস্থানসমূহকে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_031_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34148,"position":8,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না (যেন)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_031_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34149,"position":9,"arabic":"يُبْدِينَ","translation":"প্রদর্শন করে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_031_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34150,"position":10,"arabic":"زِينَتَهُنَّ","translation":"তাদের সৌন্দর্য","audioUrl":"wbw/024_031_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34151,"position":11,"arabic":"إِلَّا","tr